high_descs: turn and walk to the right side of the sink.
Pick up the fork behind the pepper mill on the counter.
Look down at the cabinet below the sink.
Open the cabinet door and place the fork on the plate.
Pick up the plate from the cabinet.
Walk over to the left side of the sink.
Put the plate down in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To put a fork on a plate and put the plate in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around, move to the sink.
Pick up the fork on the counter, right of the sink.
Bring the fork near the right cabinet under the sink.
Put the fork in the plate sitting in the right cabinet under the sink.
Pick up the plate with fork in the cabinet.
Bring the the plate left, to the left sink.
Put the plate with fork in the left sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with fork on it, in the left sink.

high_descs: Turn left, hang a left at the microwave and walk to the sink.
Pick up the fork behind the gold pepper grinder on the right side of the counter.
Look down at the cabinets under the sink.
Open the right lower cabinet under the sink and put the fork inside the pan in the cabinet.
Pick up the pan with the fork inside and close the door.
Turn around, walk towards the fridge and turn around to face the sink.
Put the pan with the fork inside the left side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a fork in a sink.
